title: BULLDOGE POOLS? 🚀 🚀 🚀
body:
You knew this moment would come.

Maybe it was just a hintergedanken. Maybe you were as sure as a doge is good. Whatever it was, you were right. 

BULLDOGE pools are coming to Dogen!!!

VOTE: should we release the BULLDOGE into the Dogen Park on Ethereum first before launching BSC farms? 

No matter the consequence? No matter the danger? Crossing the bridge without hesitation! Shall we boldly go where no doge has gone before...and let BULLDOGE loose on Ethereum?
